Volume booster for YouTube helps you boost you're YouTube video/music volume. it’s a user friendly MV3 extension that doesn’t open any tabs and asks for no extra permission.

You can enjoy you’re YouTube music/video with more than 600% volume than before.

All you need to do is to open the pop-up on you’re YouTube tab and change the volume slider.

As you all know Chrome store is changing to MV3, we are already releasing this extension in MV3 so there is no worry, we are not going to shut extension or make any changes after a while.

We respect you’re privacy so instead of asking for any access to you’re audio capture we use a different way to run the extension.

Details: 
Boost up to 600% volume on YouTube
No extra tab needed
Asking for no permission
Completely free
MV3
